ActCustoms Act
SubjectRegulations Amending Certain Regulations Made under the Customs Act (CJFTA)
PrecisRegulations Amending CERTAIN REGULATIONS MADE UNDER THE CUSTOMS ACT (CJFTA) in order to incorporate the Canada-Jordan Free Trade Agreement (CJFTA) into Canada’s existing regulatory framework by allowing customs procedures related to rules of origin to be administered in accordance with the terms of the CJFTA.
